d displayName to all marketplace plugin entries","verified_at":"2026-05-21T16:50:17Z"}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/3bf5929025edffd209d8123a68d99088b14f3767","html_url":"https://github.com/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commit/3bf5929025edffd209d8123a68d99088b14f3767","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/3bf5929025edffd209d8123a68d99088b14f3767/comments","author":{"login":"jakemmarsh","id":2916671,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI5MTY2NzE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2916671?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh","html_url":"https://github.com/jakemmarsh","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"committer":{"login":"web-flow","id":19864447,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5ODY0NDQ3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow","html_url":"https://github.com/web-flow","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/web-flow/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"parents":[{"sha":"09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be","html_url":"https://github.com/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commit/09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be"},{"sha":"66e99253885ca209ff69cc2855081bf49e8928ac","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/66e99253885ca209ff69cc2855081bf49e8928ac","html_url":"https://github.com/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commit/66e99253885ca209ff69cc2855081bf49e8928ac"}]},{"sha":"66e99253885ca209ff69cc2855081bf49e8928ac","node_id":"C_kwDOQ_-q4toAKDY2ZTk5MjUzODg1Y2EyMDlmZjY5Y2MyODU1MDgxYmY0OWU4OTI4YWM","commit":{"author":{"name":"Jake Marsh","email":"jakemarsh@anthropic.com","date":"2026-05-21T16:44:15Z"},"committer":{"name":"Jake Marsh","email":"jakemarsh@anthropic.com","date":"2026-05-21T16:44:15Z"},"message":"Drop displayName for cockroachdb to clear policy scan\n\nThe cockroachdb plugin has a cached failing policy verdict (its\nhooks/hooks.json PostToolUse hook fires on every Write|Edit|MultiEdit\nwith no project-relevance gate). Adding displayName put its entry in\nthe scan's changed set, so the cached failure blocked this PR.\n\nLeaving the cockroachdb entry byte-identical to main keeps it out of\nthe changed set so the gate passes. cockroachdb still needs its hook\nfixed upstream before it can carry a displayName.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>","tree":{"sha":"10be75c3576b5ba6c9373fb312b4101003896f1d","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/git/trees/10be75c3576b5ba6c9373fb312b4101003896f1d"},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/git/commits/66e99253885ca209ff69cc2855081bf49e8928ac","comment_count":0,"verification":{"verified":true,"reason":"valid","signature":"-----BEGIN SSH SIGNATURE-----\nU1NIU0lHAAAAAQAAAGgAAAATZWNkc2Etc2hhMi1uaXN0cDI1NgAAAAhuaXN0cDI1NgAAAE\nEEDgjCAgg09MxcMOW3gDfZIurUl59XjCbSNqH32RkkdwViDPAyRlnJWligUBIBoq7cvZdm\nLxUKKSxdIMaIeHBP+wAAAANnaXQAAAAAAAAABnNoYTUxMgAAAGQAAAATZWNkc2Etc2hhMi\n1uaXN0cDI1NgAAAEkAAAAgD9TQX/NScL9EKEOhC/3HGzce0AdK43rOST4jzT8I+sQAAAAh\nAK83+cVGG76w6agN+6bQnF4KllkMhEa14kFRjsZar7ms\n-----END SSH SIGNATURE-----","payload":"tree 10be75c3576b5ba6c9373fb312b4101003896f1d\nparent 370deb5720856196869196126da806d708219def\nauthor Jake Marsh <jakemarsh@anthropic.com> 1779381855 -0400\ncommitter Jake Marsh <jakemarsh@anthropic.com> 1779381855 -0400\n\nDrop displayName for cockroachdb to clear policy scan\n\nThe cockroachdb plugin has a cached failing policy verdict (its\nhooks/hooks.json PostToolUse hook fires on every Write|Edit|MultiEdit\nwith no project-relevance gate). Adding displayName put its entry in\nthe scan's changed set, so the cached failure blocked this PR.\n\nLeaving the cockroachdb entry byte-identical to main keeps it out of\nthe changed set so the gate passes. cockroachdb still needs its hook\nfixed upstream before it can carry a displayName.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n","verified_at":"2026-05-21T16:44:47Z"}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/66e99253885ca209ff69cc2855081bf49e8928ac","html_url":"https://github.com/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commit/66e99253885ca209ff69cc2855081bf49e8928ac","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/66e99253885ca209ff69cc2855081bf49e8928ac/comments","author":{"login":"jakemmarsh","id":2916671,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI5MTY2NzE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubus