html_url":"https://github.com/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commit/370deb5720856196869196126da806d708219def"}]},{"sha":"370deb5720856196869196126da806d708219def","node_id":"C_kwDOQ_-q4toAKDM3MGRlYjU3MjA4NTYxOTY4NjkxOTYxMjZkYTgwNmQ3MDgyMTlkZWY","commit":{"author":{"name":"Jake Marsh","email":"jakemarsh@anthropic.com","date":"2026-05-21T15:36:21Z"},"committer":{"name":"Jake Marsh","email":"jakemarsh@anthropic.com","date":"2026-05-21T15:36:21Z"},"message":"feat: add displayName to all marketplace plugin entries\n\nRender human-readable plugin names in the plugin directory instead of the\nslug-humanize fallback (\"Brand voice\", \"Cockroachdb\", \"Sp global\").\nAdds displayName to each of the 49 entries in marketplace.json.\n\nPartner plugins can still override via their own plugin.json — the consumer\nprefers a plugin's manifest displayName and falls back to the marketplace\nentry value.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>","tree":{"sha":"9c9bf1045c8f45ef099f37a3621402e0f4ef46e4","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/git/trees/9c9bf1045c8f45ef099f37a3621402e0f4ef46e4"},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/git/commits/370deb5720856196869196126da806d708219def","comment_count":0,"verification":{"verified":true,"reason":"valid","signature":"-----BEGIN SSH SIGNATURE-----\nU1NIU0lHAAAAAQAAAGgAAAATZWNkc2Etc2hhMi1uaXN0cDI1NgAAAAhuaXN0cDI1NgAAAE\nEEDgjCAgg09MxcMOW3gDfZIurUl59XjCbSNqH32RkkdwViDPAyRlnJWligUBIBoq7cvZdm\nLxUKKSxdIMaIeHBP+wAAAANnaXQAAAAAAAAABnNoYTUxMgAAAGQAAAATZWNkc2Etc2hhMi\n1uaXN0cDI1NgAAAEkAAAAhAKaMDwfvRzpZlu4SYwt9KBtWC1E2fca8Zd3+BV9OJ2ZlAAAA\nIA19aFAU4rf+nqfRVwwDLw3vNVqNCrcgzdGC3q763TfA\n-----END SSH SIGNATURE-----","payload":"tree 9c9bf1045c8f45ef099f37a3621402e0f4ef46e4\nparent 09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be\nauthor Jake Marsh <jakemarsh@anthropic.com> 1779377781 -0400\ncommitter Jake Marsh <jakemarsh@anthropic.com> 1779377781 -0400\n\nfeat: add displayName to all marketplace plugin entries\n\nRender human-readable plugin names in the plugin directory instead of the\nslug-humanize fallback (\"Brand voice\", \"Cockroachdb\", \"Sp global\").\nAdds displayName to each of the 49 entries in marketplace.json.\n\nPartner plugins can still override via their own plugin.json — the consumer\nprefers a plugin's manifest displayName and falls back to the marketplace\nentry value.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n","verified_at":"2026-05-21T15:37:43Z"}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/370deb5720856196869196126da806d708219def","html_url":"https://github.com/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commit/370deb5720856196869196126da806d708219def","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/370deb5720856196869196126da806d708219def/comments","author":{"login":"jakemmarsh","id":2916671,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI5MTY2NzE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2916671?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh","html_url":"https://github.com/jakemmarsh","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"committer":{"login":"jakemmarsh","id":2916671,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI5MTY2NzE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2916671?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh","html_url":"https://github.com/jakemmarsh","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jakemmarsh/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"parents":[{"sha":"09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be","html_url":"https://github.com/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commit/09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be"}]},{"sha":"09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be","node_id":"C_kwDOQ_-q4toAKDA5ZjYyZmI0YzA3ZWJmN2IwYmIwYWRlZDM2YmVjNGVlYmE1OWY2YmU","commit":{"author":{"name":"Tobin South","email":"tobin.south@gmail.com","date":"2026-05-19T17:36:53Z"},"committer":{"name":"GitHub","email":"noreply@github.com","date":"2026-05-19T17:36:53Z"},"message":"Fix dead MCP server URLs: deepsense rehosted, paypal moved to SSE (#239)\n\nThe Check MCP URLs workflow (after the connection-failure probe fix in\nthis PR's parent) surfaced four endpoints that fail every connection:\n\n- mcp.deepsense.ai does not resolve in DNS at all. The biorxiv, chembl,\n  and clinical_trials servers were rehosted under\n  hcls.mcp.claude.com (Anthropic MCP directory entries dated\n  2026-01-07). Paths are unchanged; only the host moved. All three\n  return a complete MCP initialize response with no auth.\n\n- mcp.paypal.com/mcp returns 404 at every path. PayPal's live endpoint\n  is /sse (SSE transport, not streamable HTTP) and returns 401 with\n  WWW-Authenticate: Bearer realm=\"OAuth\" — alive, OAuth required.\n  Their docs claim /http for streamable transport but it returns 404\n  today. Type changed http -> sse to match the actual transport.\n\nAnyone with the bio-research or small-business bundle installed gets\nconnect failures on every agent spawn until this lands.","tree":{"sha":"3ae47863ca6645d59430ff71223db37f6e315012","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/git/trees/3ae47863ca6645d59430ff71223db37f6e315012"},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/git/commits/09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be","comment_count":0,"verification":{"verified":true,"reason":"valid","signature":"-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\nwsFcBAABCAAQBQJqDJ+1CRC1aQ7uu5UhlAAAZu4QAIdhXrkYfX1uoa2ITPMrL077\nc21O1+jAwwK/bvwDmULju53dntJhGZwqqJG/ZPblN2ccrEwlrtLyyflaGP1YHMMN\nf3GisGe/QrxByk3VFdEUd+BxiEpacgVP71FTn7XMyET/IkG2xo1CzZhg5n10uAJ+\nkYL0tDnh07WW7Ogu4wHuSpFxNIqWPIwRylhhhIqI24hpOaRiFAA9wanKPYgUjyBy\n38vpwBatPTvcD+It96DtRhp7OFWMI4zwdc3wv2dK+MRJ1NQN5qJMCp/dRTH3C+3c\n5rbgBUreqGqiMoBdp6XpDqFfP7cnW7EvUd1dNiO77VZV/uzDwCIBJb2MtZsjnoLT\n6sWO+3JJtvBE6CAEziP7MBzfR2nEh6WiyGXq133PGhn/zdVPGV8hDguGrhM8PycB\neCl87CZjaP9QCjDjIJ8wWvGebbbdbDPmNBDTAEP8UfQ1eajdMUC3pzhLKiLKl/Af\n3s8gu0HQzioR2tx6CHZHqXdgTU3qqwE4AmIyOKcWYZ0SuOW2rApzNRCJnDmlx+Lv\no6oVDPxjgcsz/PVEginBvfSuLY7Fc4w2Z+L81w8jYI34Fh3FTgqi+OTGGVdpKlvh\nlF1mpXOywyUZZEGNOz8GwKdB80Td52ZeUQeqbNZIASqX5DNB/INXRRZV5M37jDal\nhm0A30u/aMFVQgtsxMN6\n=Q2Z1\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----\n","payload":"tree 3ae47863ca6645d59430ff71223db37f6e315012\nparent 2ba85d9732f417c5f83d02a487b71e252187cd73\nauthor Tobin South <tobin.south@gmail.com> 1779212213 -0700\ncommitter GitHub <noreply@github.com> 1779212213 -0700\n\nFix dead MCP server URLs: deepsense rehosted, paypal moved to SSE (#239)\n\nThe Check MCP URLs workflow (after the connection-failure probe fix in\nthis PR's parent) surfaced four endpoints that fail every connection:\n\n- mcp.deepsense.ai does not resolve in DNS at all. The biorxiv, chembl,\n  and clinical_trials servers were rehosted under\n  hcls.mcp.claude.com (Anthropic MCP directory entries dated\n  2026-01-07). Paths are unchanged; only the host moved. All three\n  return a complete MCP initialize response with no auth.\n\n- mcp.paypal.com/mcp returns 404 at every path. PayPal's live endpoint\n  is /sse (SSE transport, not streamable HTTP) and returns 401 with\n  WWW-Authenticate: Bearer realm=\"OAuth\" — alive, OAuth required.\n  Their docs claim /http for streamable transport but it returns 404\n  today. Type changed http -> sse to match the actual transport.\n\nAnyone with the bio-research or small-business bundle installed gets\nconnect failures on every agent spawn until this lands.","verified_at":"2026-05-19T17:36:54Z"}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be","html_url":"https://github.com/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commit/09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins/commits/09f62fb4c07ebf7b0bb0aded36bec4eeba59f6be/comments","author":{"login":"tobinsouth","id":32489862,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMyNDg5ODYy","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/32489862?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/tobinsouth","html_url":"https://github.com/tobinsouth","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tobinsouth/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tobinsouth/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tobinsouth/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tobinsouth/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tobinsouth/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/to